      "abstract": "The GAD-7 is a 7-item self-report screening tool and severity measure for generalized anxiety disorder. Items are rated on a 4-point scale assessing symptom frequency over the past two weeks. Brief, reliable, and widely used in primary care and research settings for anxiety assessment.",
